     language specified in tooltypes/Shell (locale name if available or
     `"english"').

`@pretend'
     state of `pretend' (dry run mode) flag: 0-Real, 1-Pretend.

`@special-msg'
     custom fatal error message.

`@user-level'
     0-Novice, 1-Average, 2-Expert.


